title: RCA Reno 16GB, Android 10, 4G LTE Unlocked Smartphone (Silver)
features: RCA, the American brand with a legacy of 100 years, has been to make the smartphone valuable and accessible to all.

Dual SIM unlocked for the freedom to choose your preferred GSM carrier. Compatible with T-Mobile and carriers using T-Mobile network. (***Not compatible with AT&T, Cricket Wireless or with CDMA Networks like Verizon, Sprint, and Boost Mobile***) SIM cards not included.
5.0” IPS Display featuring a 18: 9 Aspect ratio with FREE protective case and attached screen protector.
Newest Android 10 with 16GB Internal memory, and an optional MircoSD card with up to 128 GB capacity.
Featured with face unlock, 8 MP autofocus camera with LED Flash with a 5 MP selfie camera.

4G LTE/VoLTE: (2/4/5/12/17/66), 3G: (850/1900). No long term contracts required; International version, available in Canada, Mexico, Colombia, Jamaica, Venezuela, Argentina, and other 190 countries and regions.

2000 mAh battery (up to 2 days) for standby and backup. Browse, stream music, watch video, and play games at blazing speed. Can be used with Wi-Fi Network only, WiFi mobile hotspot, GPS for navigation and location services.
Box Content: Phone, Charger, Cable, Protective Case, Screen protector (attached), Headset, Quick Start Guides, User Manual.
Comes with 1 year US based warranty service.
description: With the most recent version of Android 10, this will make phone even more simple, personal and helpful—including easier access to users favorite content. ***New package includes: phone, charger, headphones, USB cord, screen protector (Attached), battery, user manual, quick start guide, and FREE protective case. US compatibility on T-Mobile Networks (***Not compatible with AT&T, Cricket or with CDMA networks like Verizon, Sprint, and Boost Mobile).
